@startuml
title Add a New Car (Admin Flow)

actor Admin
participant "Car Service" as CarService
database DB

== Admin adds a new car ==

Admin -> CarService: AddCar(make, model, year, vin, color, km, dailyPrice)
note right: Admin provides all car details
CarService -> DB: INSERT INTO cars(...)
DB --> CarService: carId
CarService --> Admin: success response { carId, message }

== Result ==
note over DB
New car record created:
- carId
- make, model, year
- vin, color, km
- dailyPrice
- status = "AVAILABLE"
end note
@enduml
